{
  "title": "Tender Tropical Brazilian Kabanos Stew",
  "description": "A light and floral Brazilian dish featuring Polish kabanos, perfect for a sick day, made with coconut cream and cooked in a cataplana vessel, this kosher friendly stew is a unique fusion of flavors.",
