      "amount": "1/2 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the cataplana vessel over medium heat and add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the kabanos and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the chicken broth, diced tomatoes, coconut cream, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes or until the kabanos are tender.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and lime juice.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
